Subject: [PATCH 13/13] Implement ESP GCM and NLB enc-hs-key handling

Add RFC4106 AES-GCM ESP encrypt/decrypt for GlobalProtect gateways,
recognize aes128gcm8/12/16 ICV variants, and implement NLB enc-hs-key
blob parsing with TLS 1.2 session-key decipherment for tunnel-opaque.
